OL,3,CHouse explosion which hospitalised
OL,4,Cfour people caused by gas build-up
OL,6,FAn explosion which destroyed a family
OL,7,Fhome in Jersey was caused by gas.
OL,9,FFour people were hospitalised after
OL,10,Fthe major incident at Mont Pinel, St
OL,11,FSaviour, in June with the Fire Service
OL,12,Fnow stating it is "reasonable to
OL,13,Fconclude that an explosion occured due
OL,14,Fto ignition of a mixture of a
OL,15,Fflammable gas and air that accumulated
OL,16,Fwithin the property".
OL,18,FIt follows an initial investigation by
OL,19,Fthe island's Health and Safety
OL,20,FInspectorate which is still continuing
OL,21,Finto why the incident took place.
