OL,3,CHouse explosion which hospitalised
OL,4,Cfour people caused by gas build-up
OL,6,FIt says households and businesses will
OL,7,Fsoon receive a letter with more
OL,8,Finformation about visits and procedure.
OL,10,FITV News has sought to get further
OL,11,Fclarification on the type of gas that
OL,12,Fis being referred to as the cause of
OL,13,Fthe explosion but all requests to the
OL,14,FGovernment of Jersey and Island Energy
OL,15,Ffor interviews and more information
OL,16,Fhave been refused.
